|---------|---------|--------|-------|
| Chrome | ≥90 | ✅ Full | Best performance |
| Firefox | ≥88 | ✅ Full | IndexedDB quota limits |
| Safari | ≥14 | ✅ Full | Requires polyfills |
| Edge | ≥90 | ✅ Full | Chromium-based |
| Opera | ≥76 | ✅ Full | Chromium-based |
